headline.main: Bellew Stuns Heavyweight Haye With 11th-Round Stoppage
headline.print_headline: Bellew Stuns Heavyweight Haye With 11th-Round Stoppage

lead_paragraph: Tony Bellew caused a huge upset by moving up to the heavyweight class and stopping an injured David Haye in the 11th round in a gripping, all-British fight at the O2 Arena on Saturday.
